BackupPC-XS version 0.30
========================

BackupPC::XS implements various BackupPC functions in a perl-callable
module.  This module is required for BackupPC V4+.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

